This folder contains the code for producing the result of method “Spatial_2” in the paper.
The full details about this method can be found in the following article.


Wang A, Wang K, Tsung F. Statistical surface monitoring by spatial-structure modeling. Journal of Quality Technology. 2014:46(4);359-376.


Instructions:

1. Run the “historical_maker.m” to generate in-control data : beta_historical.csv and theta_historical.csv



2. Run ARL_out_of_control.m for each of shift scenario
